	<text>
		<body xml:lang="en">
			<div>

	<pb n="0001" facs="liv_001277_0001"/><!--pb/@n='1'-->
<lb/><p rend="right"><placeName>Birkenhead</placeName></p>
<lb/><p rend="right">6 March 1858 </p>
<lb/><p>My Dear <persName>D<hi rend="sup"><hi rend="underline">r</hi></hi> Raffles</persName></p>
<lb/><p>I have not 
<lb/>been very well 
<lb/>for some days 
<lb/>from a complaint 
<lb/>the result of 

	<pb n="0002" facs="liv_001277_0002"/><!--pb/@n='2'--> 
<lb/>African fever 
<lb/>and the river being 
<lb/>so very rough 
<lb/>this afternoon 
<lb/>I have very 
<lb/>unwillingly 
<lb/>yielded to the 
<lb/>suggestion of 
<lb/>my wife not 

	<pb n="0003" facs="liv_001277_0003"/><!--pb/@n='3'--> 
<lb/>to expose myself 
<lb/>tonight. I have 
<lb/>been hard at 
<lb/>work all day &amp; 
<lb/>made quite too late for dinner 
<lb/>and but for 
<lb/>what I mention 
<lb/>would have 
<lb/>felt it a <choice><sic>privelege</sic><corr>privilege</corr></choice>
<lb/>to spend the 
<lb/>evening with 
<lb/>you &amp; the <persName>Crossfields</persName>

	<pb n="0004" facs="liv_001277_0004"/><!--pb/@n='4'--> 
<lb/>I hope you will 
<lb/>kindly excuse 
<lb/>me. I shall 
<lb/>come over tomorrow 
<lb/>and bid you 
<lb/>farewell - after 
<lb/>worship<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p>Hoping you will 
<lb/>not be annoyed by 
<lb/>this unexpected failure 
<lb/>of an engagement<reg>.</reg></p>
<lb/><p>I am &amp;c </p>
<lb/><p>David Livingstone </p>
			
</div>
